天室的名称按照数字排序，统称「 N 号房」。2020 年 3 月底，韩国警方成立案件专门调查组对案件展开调查，12 月底，韩国警方「网络性犯罪调查本部」公布，在 9 个月的时间内共调查 3575 名嫌疑人并拘押其中的 245 人。警方深入调查的同时，韩国法院也在对案件进行审理并陆续宣判。@环球网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc1f9825f8443a036b5ea7435a23cfcc_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "297 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453540321"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IybbylNbxyPcBEAMaCDYzMDY2MjU0IM3HuoMGMAQ4rgJADHIJNDUzNTQwMzIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1617937782.7052135", "card_id": "Q_453465762", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待美国费米实验室的最新 μ 子试验结果？粒子的标准模型是否存在被「推翻」的风险？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "相关结果的公布网页：First results from Fermilab ’ s Muon g-2 experiment strengthen evidence of new physics"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b1694a31cb374f3923126102fe39033b_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "201 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453465762"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IybbylNbxyPcBEAMaCDYzMDQ5NjgwIJS+t4MGMAc43AZADXIJNDUzNDY1NzYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1617937782.7057855", "card_id": "EV_12216975", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《进击的巨人》漫画完结，你有哪些「意难平」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/100/v2-452de138c1cd10602ac3aedd5fd63243_fhd.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "199 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/special/1363226098357075968"}}, "attached_info": "CnwIybbylNbxyPcBEBgaBDYwNjAg4Zq7gwZADnIIMTIyMTY5NzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBMWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS9zcGVja